io.netty.handler.codec.http2

Class Http2OutboundFrameLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.netty.handler.codec.http2.Http2OutboundFrameLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.netty.handler.codec.http2.Http2DataWriter, io.netty.handler.codec.http2.Http2FrameWriter, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @UnstableApi
public class Http2OutboundFrameLogger
extends Object
implements io.netty.handler.codec.http2.Http2FrameWriter
    Decorator around a Http2FrameWriter that logs all outbound frames before calling the writer.
